<br>
We get a buff that when casted on a person PREVENTS them from being summoned by anyone/anything.<br>
<br>
It isn't too out of line with the type of spells we have already. If it is a buff instead of a summoned item it would make mages NEEDED on raids a lot more often.<br>
<br>
It would make it a lot easier for pullers to bring the mobs to the group, it would also prevent mobs from gate/summoning to way off in the zone, would help with mobs random summoning people (ssra) etc.<br>
<br>
Downside would be no more emergency COH the puller to save his life, if a mob can't summon then neither can we. But it would save lives a lot more often than the rare COH  me NOW please! calls we get.<br>
<br>
It would be nice if we could summon mobs to us, if we were on their hate list or something then when they gate we could pull them back with no trains or even pull mobs from a distance. But it would be easily abused. Lol nothing like running to Maestro, casting malosi/mala then getting COH out of ag range back to group then summoning  Maestro to group for fight halfway across the zone.<br>
<br>
I  think it would be more feasable for us to get a buff that keeps people from being summoned, what are your thoughts? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uxreynnx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>x Reynn x</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#333333>(5/23/02 6:33:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=210.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: no summon</span><hr size=1> 1.  I would like a longer duration DS.<br>
